ConstValues.value: "Are you sure you want to cancel the transaction ?"

"
  • Please select the Bank in which you have an account.
    Onproceed you will be redirected to Bank's Webview where you will be required to enter your Account number or Bank Card number as the case maybe and your email address.
  • Further you will be prompted to enter OTP received on your registered Mobile phone number.
    On successful validation of the OTP you will be registered with the Bank for transaction.
    At this stage your payment will be initiated and you will be prompted to enter a 2nd OTP you would receive, to approve the payment.
  • On successful validation the Payment will be completed.
    In case you already had a bank previously entered and you choose the same bank to make payment, in this case you will be redirected to Bank's Webview and you will be prompted to enter OTP you would receive on your registered phone number, to complete the payment, so it will be a one click checkout.
  • Minimum amount for this Paymentmode is IDR 10000.
